The majority of the data where collected at the University of Potsdam at the end of a lecture on inclusive education.



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code .hidden}
dat_subjects %>% 
  count(group, uni) %>% 
  pivot_wider(names_from = group, values_from = n) %>%
  mutate(across(1:3, ~replace_na(.x, 0))) %>%
  bind_rows("a" = summarise(., 
    across(1, ~"Total" ),
    across(2:3, ~(sum(.x)))
  )) %>%
  mutate(Total = Training + Control) %>%
  nice_table(
    spanner = list("Group condition" = 2:4), 
    cols_label = list(uni = "University"),
    title = "Place of data collection",
    file = "tab-sample.docx"
  ) 
```

